day-to-day choices we make.

00:24:39.820 --> 00:24:41.860 align:middle line:84%
So we can change our
attitude and at least

00:24:41.860 --> 00:24:44.040 align:middle line:84%
get to a more neutral,
accepting place with it.

00:24:44.040 --> 00:24:45.580 align:middle line:90%
And that saves a lot of energy.

00:24:45.580 --> 00:24:48.100 align:middle line:84%
We're not draining energy
through this stressful reaction

00:24:48.100 --> 00:24:48.770 align:middle line:90%
to it.

00:24:48.770 --> 00:24:51.070 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: So then
that affects, then--

00:24:51.070 --> 00:24:52.800 align:middle line:84%
you're saying that
her experience of that

00:24:52.800 --> 00:24:56.350 align:middle line:84%
and all sorts of people, just
different experiences of things

00:24:56.350 --> 00:24:59.181 align:middle line:90%
affects, then, our environment.

00:24:59.181 --> 00:25:00.930 align:middle line:84%
>>MARTIN: It affects
our own energy field.

00:25:00.930 --> 00:25:03.760 align:middle line:84%
That energy field relates
to the larger energy field,

00:25:03.760 --> 00:25:05.620 align:middle line:90%
so we're contributing to that.

00:25:05.620 --> 00:25:07.820 align:middle line:84%
As more and more people
start making these choices

00:25:07.820 --> 00:25:10.720 align:middle line:84%
within themselves to not go
through the same old reactive

00:25:10.720 --> 00:25:13.330 align:middle line:84%
patterns that we've gone through
for a long time, that they've

00:25:13.330 --> 00:25:16.130 align:middle line:84%
