00:25:16.130 --> 00:25:17.670 align:middle line:90%
and to be something different.

00:25:17.670 --> 00:25:20.140 align:middle line:84%
Then, collectively
as we do that,

00:25:20.140 --> 00:25:22.220 align:middle line:84%
it begins to put out a
larger field of energy

00:25:22.220 --> 00:25:24.250 align:middle line:90%
that impacts the Earth itself.

00:25:24.250 --> 00:25:26.920 align:middle line:84%
And the Earth's energy fields,
we know, they impact us.

00:25:26.920 --> 00:25:28.500 align:middle line:84%
And so there's a
relationship there.

00:25:28.500 --> 00:25:30.690 align:middle line:84%
It's all part of the
most important things,

00:25:30.690 --> 00:25:34.150 align:middle line:84%
I think, we all do to contribute
to changing the world.

00:25:34.150 --> 00:25:36.860 align:middle line:84%
They're the things we need to
do with the organizations we're

00:25:36.860 --> 00:25:39.040 align:middle line:84%
