day-to-day lives

00:25:46.184 --> 00:25:47.100 align:middle line:90%
on the internal level?

00:25:47.100 --> 00:25:47.860 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: In our own hearts.

00:25:47.860 --> 00:25:49.230 align:middle line:90%
>>MARTIN: In our own hearts.

00:25:49.230 --> 00:25:51.610 align:middle line:84%
