00:26:55.505 --> 00:26:57.094 align:middle line:90%
What can change consciousness?

00:26:57.094 --> 00:26:58.760 align:middle line:84%
The way I see the
model working in a way

00:26:58.760 --> 00:27:00.820 align:middle line:84%
is you have changing
consciousness, which

00:27:00.820 --> 00:27:03.990 align:middle line:84%
impacts changes in the
psychological paradigms,

00:27:03.990 --> 00:27:06.180 align:middle line:90%
