00:27:06.180 --> 00:27:07.790 align:middle line:84%
As those begin to
shift and change,

00:27:07.790 --> 00:27:10.513 align:middle line:84%
then that filters down into
the various systems that

00:27:10.513 --> 00:27:13.130 align:middle line:84%
