consciousness, then

00:27:19.240 --> 00:27:21.040 align:middle line:84%
it feeds back down
to the system.

00:27:21.040 --> 00:27:22.530 align:middle line:84%
And I think that's
what people are

00:27:22.530 --> 00:27:25.560 align:middle line:84%
aspiring to do, many now, in
this era, which generically

00:27:25.560 --> 00:27:26.770 align:middle line:90%
been called "the shift."

00:27:26.770 --> 00:27:29.140 align:middle line:84%
How do we create a
change in consciousness

00:27:29.140 --> 00:27:31.564 align:middle line:84%
