00:35:52.930 --> 00:35:56.444 align:middle line:84%
And I think that
patience, letting

00:35:56.444 --> 00:35:57.860 align:middle line:84%
scientists do what
scientists need

00:35:57.860 --> 00:36:00.399 align:middle line:84%
to do to unfold this
