to my heart.

00:44:34.830 --> 00:44:38.000 align:middle line:84%
I can say that I feel like,
yeah, I'm growing-- still

00:44:38.000 --> 00:44:40.380 align:middle line:84%
growing like everyone
else, but I'm certainly

00:44:40.380 --> 00:44:42.916 align:middle line:84%
less emotionally reactive
than I've ever been.

00:44:42.916 --> 00:44:43.790 align:middle line:90%
I'm certainly kinder.

00:44:43.790 --> 00:44:45.485 align:middle line:84%
I'm certainly more
compassionate.

00:44:45.485 --> 00:44:46.110 align:middle line:90%
I'm certainly--

00:44:46.110 --> 00:44:46.970 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Funnier.

00:44:46.970 --> 00:44:47.970 align:middle line:90%
>>MARTIN: Maybe funnier.

00:44:47.970 --> 00:44:50.174 align:middle line:90%
Maybe even better looking.

00:44:50.174 --> 00:44:50.840 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Exactly.

00:44:50.840 --> 00:44:52.548 align:middle line:84%
>>MARTIN: I have to
be careful, because I

00:44:52.548 --> 00:44:55.840 align:middle line:84%
