00:44:57.785 --> 00:44:58.570 align:middle line:90%
>>MARTIN: That's right.

00:44:58.570 --> 00:44:59.820 align:middle line:90%
But a lot of things like that.

00:44:59.820 --> 00:45:03.940 align:middle line:84%
And I think it's hard to
