is very different,

00:45:05.710 --> 00:45:08.110 align:middle line:84%
the way I perceive things,
the way I perceive myself,

00:45:08.110 --> 00:45:10.160 align:middle line:84%
others, the world
itself, is certainly

00:45:10.160 --> 00:45:12.131 align:middle line:84%
very different than
what it would have been.

00:45:12.131 --> 00:45:13.630 align:middle line:84%
And I think what's
exciting about it

00:45:13.630 --> 00:45:18.840 align:middle line:84%
to me, Lisa, is that my life
does not have a ceiling on it,

00:45:18.840 --> 00:45:21.060 align:middle line:84%
whereas many people my
age, by now, they've

00:45:21.060 --> 00:45:21.852 align:middle line:90%
