00:45:43.422 --> 00:45:44.380 align:middle line:90%
And that's a real gift.

00:45:44.380 --> 00:45:45.980 align:middle line:84%
And that's part of what
I mean by awareness.

00:45:45.980 --> 00:45:48.271 align:middle line:84%
It's sometimes harder to
describe the gift of awareness

00:45:48.271 --> 00:45:48.970 align:middle line:90%
that you have.

