00:46:14.512 --> 00:46:15.470 align:middle line:90%
>>MARTIN: Occurs, yeah.

00:46:15.470 --> 00:46:16.390 align:middle line:90%
I was looking at heart rhythms.

00:46:16.390 --> 00:46:18.890 align:middle line:84%
Remember, the stuff we talked
about earlier about heart rate

00:46:18.890 --> 00:46:21.420 align:middle line:84%
