00:52:31.850 --> 00:52:33.020 align:middle line:90%
>>MARTIN: Three steps.

00:52:33.020 --> 00:52:34.790 align:middle line:90%
Close your eyes, please.

00:52:34.790 --> 00:52:37.025 align:middle line:84%
First step is
called heart focus.

00:52:37.025 --> 00:52:39.655 align:middle line:84%
I just want you to shift, like
feel the energy coming down

00:52:39.655 --> 00:52:41.780 align:middle line:84%
from your head right into
the center of your chest,

00:52:41.780 --> 00:52:45.210 align:middle line:90%
into the area of the heart.

00:52:45.210 --> 00:52:48.330 align:middle line:84%
And just focus your attention
there, casually and gently.

00:52:48.330 --> 00:52:54.934 align:middle line:90%


00:52:54.934 --> 00:52:56.350 align:middle line:84%
And now what I'd
like you to do is

00:52:56.350 --> 00:53:00.875 align:middle line:84%
I'd like you to begin to
breathe naturally and normally,

00:53:00.875 --> 00:53:05.820 align:middle line:84%
