of your chest.

00:53:10.970 --> 00:53:12.925 align:middle line:84%
And that's called
heart-focused breathing.

00:53:12.925 --> 00:53:26.380 align:middle line:90%


00:53:26.380 --> 00:53:28.430 align:middle line:84%
Nice deep breaths, in and
out through the center

00:53:28.430 --> 00:53:29.140 align:middle line:90%
