00:53:29.140 --> 00:53:32.260 align:middle line:90%
Heart-focused breathing.

00:53:32.260 --> 00:53:33.880 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: I can feel my heartbeat.

00:53:33.880 --> 00:53:35.950 align:middle line:90%
>>MARTIN: Good.

00:53:35.950 --> 00:53:37.825 align:middle line:84%
I want you to maintain
